{
  "stem": "11296.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they called me to the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the barracks they had an office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They called me in there, and my heart was beating like a horse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said to myself, what's going to happen to you, Bella, now?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So Bella-- so he said to go back to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're going to shave my head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had already a little hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Was already, you know-- I was already this-- probably seven, eight months, and I had already good clothes wearing because I was working-- every day I put on some other things.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I sold them, and I put on old ones, and I left the old ones, and I put on new ones.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he said, you are no more going to this kommando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You're going back there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They're going to cut your hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They're going to do just like in the beginning they did to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I'm going to go work outside kommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside kommando there was, again, to the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, thank God they didn't kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to other, you know, all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, I had you know-- I knew already people, so after a few weeks of working outside I got myself into another kommando in the camp, in another kommando.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was already the end of 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my other sisters-- my sister, my other friends-- all of them had already places where to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was going until 1940-- so, I mean, in the beginning of 1944 they start building-- putting together a new kommando.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A kommando-- we didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said to everyone stay closer, we was between.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, we're going to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
